steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"fu6pl","text":"Log into Bankit with UCSF username and password:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"48e2r","text":"    - Follow this link: https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/WebSub/?form=history\u0026tool=genbank","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3i80c","text":"    - Choose more login options and select University of California, San Francisco","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"f277l","text":"Sequence Authors:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":17}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c0s0d","text":"List all sequence authors (use the Add button for more than one)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8sju8","text":"Reference Information #1:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":25}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c4k8j","text":"Select publication status (unpublished, in-press, or Published)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c7klk","text":"    - If in-press add reference title, journal title, year, volume, issue, and page numbers","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"88tke","text":"    - If published add reference title, journal title, year, volume, issue, page numbers, and PubMed ID","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fqjj4","text":"    - Optional: if unpublished add reference title","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8q6qb","text":"Select reference authors as \"Same as Sequence Authors\" or \"Specify New Authors\"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9ij2b","text":"    - If specify new authors, list authors","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7d5hd","text":"(Optional) Add Another Reference:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":33}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1mnrl","text":"Follow Reference Information #1 steps","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"arfhi","text":"Sequencing Technology:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":22}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4sljf","text":"Select the sequencing technology (or other and specify)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8mlbk","text":"Select unassembled sequence reads or assembled sequences (consisting of two or more sequence reads)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d3bvv","text":"List assembly program and version or date","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a601q","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ea6um","text":"Example: Illumina, Geneious v. Geneious Prime 2023.0.1","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":0,"length":9}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"fbfa8","text":"Submission Release Date:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":24}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3veap","text":"Select \"Immediately after processing\" or \"Release date\" ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4gd99","text":"    - If Release Date is selected, specify date in DD-Mon-YYYY format","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1j506","text":"Sequence(s) and Definition Line(s):","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":35}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"en7n","text":"Choose molecule type, linear or circular, if it is a complete sequence, and fasta or alignment format","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bahq9","text":"Either download sequence file or copy and paste it in the box","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ddmrr","text":"    - Note: make sure the first line follows this format; make everything in bold specific to your submission","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"91rpi","text":"            \u003eSeq#[organism=genus species] species straininfo","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":16,"length":1},{"style":"bold","offset":27,"length":13},{"style":"bold","offset":42,"length":18}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6g6sd","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ccpvn","text":"Example: \u003eSeq1[organism=Enterovirus rhinovirus] Rhinovirus C17 strain RvC17/USA/2019","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":0,"length":9}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ia4g","text":"Source Modifiers:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":17}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6ar2","text":"Choose organelle/location if applicable","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4ol1j","text":"Choose source modifiers and list information in value column, add as many as desired","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5jptu","text":" ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5orvj","text":"Example: Strain = RvC17/USA/2019, host = homo sapiens, tissue_type = Lung, country = USA, collection_date = 2019","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":0,"length":9}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"e2dp4","text":"Features (Overview):","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":20}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1orj5","text":"Select \"Add features by completing input forms\"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3j0k9","text":"Select \"Coding Region (CDS) / Gene / mRNA\"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"df998","text":"Select \"providing intervals\"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"qvme","text":"Click Add","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"c1d87","text":"Features (Detail): ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":19}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"aqgbf","text":"Choose if the CDS is on the + or - strand","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"aahuu","text":"If the CDS is not compete, select 5' or 3' for which end it is incomplete at","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bbnpk","text":"Select \"Entire Sequence\" or \"Specific Spans\" for Nucleotide Interval Spans","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"b03p7","text":"    - If Specific Spans, specify start and stop and which strand it is on","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6gjmh","text":"List protein name (optional: also list protein description and EC number)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c8ifp","text":"Click accept","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e5art","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"95mcn","text":"Example:  specific spans: start = 19 stop = 6498 strand = -minus; protein name = polyprotein","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":0,"length":10}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ctkvm","text":"Review Submission:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":18}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"akcf6","text":"Make sure everything looks good","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"dbub3","text":"If resubmitting check the box under the resubmission section","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
